   "source": [
    "# 04 - 多元线性回归与特征工程\n",
    "\n",
    "**目标**: 掌握多元线性回归、特征工程、特征缩放和正则化\n",
    "\n",
    "**预计时间**: 3-4 小时\n",
    "\n",
    "**前置知识**: 简单线性回归 (03_linear_regression.ipynb)\n",
    "\n",
    "---"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. 导入库"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "import seaborn as sns\n",
    "from sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split\n",
    "from sklearn.linear_model import LinearRegression, Ridge, Lasso\n",
    "from sklearn.preprocessing import StandardScaler, PolynomialFeatures\n",
    "from sklearn.metrics import mean_squared_error, r2_score\n",
    "from sklearn.datasets import fetch_california_housing\n",
    "\n",
    "# 设置中文显示\n",
    "plt.rcParams['font.sans-serif'] = ['SimHei', 'DejaVu Sans']\n",
    "plt.rcParams['axes.unicode_minus'] = False\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"库导入成功！\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2. 多元线性回归原理\n",
    "\n",
    "### 数学模型\n",
    "\n",
    "当有多个特征时，模型扩展为：\n",
    "\n",
    "$$y = w_1x_1 + w_2x_2 + ... + w_nx_n + b$$\n",
    "\n",
    "向量形式：\n",
    "\n",
    "$$y = \\mathbf{w}^T\\mathbf{x} + b$$\n",
    "\n",
    "其中：\n",
    "- $\\mathbf{x} = [x_1, x_2, ..., x_n]$ : 特征向量\n",
    "- $\\mathbf{w} = [w_1, w_2, ..., w_n]$ : 权重向量\n",
    "- $b$ : 偏置\n",
    "\n",
    "### 矩阵形式\n",
    "\n",
    "对于 $m$ 个样本：\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\\mathbf{y} = \\mathbf{X}\\mathbf{w} + b$$\n",
    "\n",
    "其中 $\\mathbf{X}$ 是 $m \\times n$ 的设计矩阵"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 3. 加载真实数据集：California Housing"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 加载 California Housing 数据集\n",
    "housing = fetch_california_housing()\n",
    "\n",
    "# 创建 DataFrame\n",
    "df = pd.DataFrame(housing.data, columns=housing.feature_names)\n",
    "df['Price'] = housing.target * 100000  # 转换为实际价格\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"数据集信息:\")\n",
    "print(f\"样本数: {df.shape[0]}\")\n",
    "print(f\"特征数: {df.shape[1] - 1}\")\n",
    "print(f\"\\n特征名称:\")\n",
    "for i, name in enumerate(housing.feature_names, 1):\n",
    "    print(f\"  {i}. {name}\")\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"\\n目标变量: 房价中位数 (单位: 美元)\")\n",
    "print(f\"\\n数据预览:\")\n",
    "print(df.head())"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 数据统计摘要\n",
    "print(\"统计摘要:\")\n",
    "print(df.describe())"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 4. 探索性数据分析 (EDA)"
   ]
  },
  {
